  <entry>
    <title>关于记忆面包</title>
    <link href="/memory-bread/2026/07/07/hello-world/"/>
    <url>/memory-bread/2026/07/07/hello-world/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="记忆中一味"><a href="#记忆中一味" class="headerlink" title="记忆中一味"></a>记忆中一味</h1><p>我们相信，好吃不是迎合出来的。</p><p>来自云南偏远农村，小时候能吃到好东西是一种奢侈。城里老师给孩子吃的手撕面包，那个画面至今记得。</p><p>现在，我们成为妈妈，孩子也爱甜食面食。我们认真学习烘焙，研究各种材料，才发现市面上太多产品并没有看起来那么美好。</p><p><strong>好，一定是走在前的。</strong></p><p>我们的理念很简单：</p><ul><li>🥖 好食材，透明配料</li><li>🔥 公开热量，知情选择</li><li>💚 回归身体本身的好吃</li><li>🤝 收集记忆中的味道</li></ul><p>不迎合低价口味，不妥协于效率成本。<br>每一款出品，都是我们愿意每天吃、放心给孩子吃的东西。</p><p>欢迎留言告诉我们你的需求，也欢迎分享你记忆中的味道。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>云南百花蜜全麦面包</title>
    <link href="/memory-bread/2026/07/05/honey-whole-wheat-bread/"/>
    <url>/memory-bread/2026/07/05/honey-whole-wheat-bread/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>.product-detail { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 24px 80px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; }.product-back { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6B6B6B; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 48px; transition: color 0.2s; }.product-back:hover { color: #0A0A0A; }.product-header { margin-bottom: 64px; }.product-eyebrow { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #C4713B; margin-bottom: 12px; }.product-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }.product-intro { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #6B6B6B; }.product-meta-bar { display: flex; gap: 40px; padding: 24px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); margin: 40px 0; }.product-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }.product-meta-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #6B6B6B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }.product-meta-value { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; }.section-label { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B6B6B; margin-bottom: 24px; }.section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 32px; }.ingredients-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }.ingredient-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); font-size: 0.9rem; }.ingredient-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); }.ingredient-name { font-weight: 400; }.ingredient-amount { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #6B6B6B; }.calorie-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }.calorie-box { background: #F0EDE8; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }.calorie-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: #C4713B; }.calorie-unit { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; margin-top: 4px; }.steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }.step { display: flex; gap: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }.step-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #C4713B; min-width: 24px; }.impressions { margin-top: 80px; padding-top: 64px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); }.impression-card { background: #F0EDE8; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; border-left: 3px solid #C4713B; }.impression-quote { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }.impression-author { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6B6B6B; }.feedback-cta { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; }.feedback-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.15); color: #0A0A0A; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem; transition: all 0.25s; }.feedback-link:hover { border-color: #0A0A0A; background: #0A0A0A; color: #FAF9F7; }</style><div class="product-detail">  <a href="/" class="product-back">← 返回首页</a>  <div class="product-header">    <div class="product-eyebrow">全麦 · 蜂蜜 · 欧包</div>    <h1 class="product-title">云南百花蜜<br>全麦面包</h1>    <p class="product-intro">小时候在农村，蜂蜜是稀罕物。舅妈家养了几窝土蜂，每年秋天收割一次，那香味——至今没有哪瓶工业蜂蜜能比。这款面包用云南百花蜜代替普通糖，蜜香浓郁，全麦口感扎实却不硬。</p>  </div>  <div class="product-meta-bar">    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">价格</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">¥38</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">热量</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">245 kcal / 100g</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">类型</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">欧包</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">份量</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">约400g/个</span>    </div>  </div>  <div class="ingredients">    <div class="section-label">配料</div>    <h2 class="section-title">每一项都有依据</h2>    <div class="ingredients-list">      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">高筋全麦粉</span><span class="ingredient-amount">300g · 保留麸皮，营养更全</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">云南百花蜜</span><span class="ingredient-amount">40g · 土蜂蜜，蜜香自然</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">鲜酵母</span><span class="ingredient-amount">8g · 比干酵母风味更好</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">盐</span><span class="ingredient-amount">5g · 提味</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">水</span><span class="ingredient-amount">220g · 冰水，面团更弹</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">特级初榨橄榄油</span><span class="ingredient-amount">15g · 冷榨进口</span></div>    </div>  </div>  <div style="margin-top: 64px;">    <div class="section-label">热量参考</div>    <div class="calorie-grid">      <div class="calorie-box">        <div class="calorie-num">245</div>        <div class="calorie-unit">kcal / 100g</div>      </div>      <div class="calorie-box">        <div class="calorie-num">980</div>        <div class="calorie-unit">kcal / 整份（约400g）</div>      </div>    </div>    <p style="font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6B6B6B; margin-top: 12px;">* 参考值，实际切割大小会有差异</p>  </div>  <div style="margin-top: 64px;">    <div class="section-label">制作步骤</div>    <div class="steps">      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">01</span><span><strong>混合</strong> — 面粉+盐+酵母（别让酵母直接碰到盐），加入水和橄榄油，搅拌成团</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">02</span><span><strong>揉面</strong> — 揉8分钟至光滑，拉伸有膜但不破</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">03</span><span><strong>一发</strong> — 室温（26℃）发酵1小时，至2倍大</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">04</span><span><strong>整形</strong> — 排气，分割成2份，滚圆松弛15分钟</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">05</span><span><strong>整形入篮</strong> — 整成长棍或圆型，接口朝下放入发酵篮</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">06</span><span><strong>二发</strong> — 冷藏（4℃）过夜，8-12小时</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">07</span><span><strong>烘烤</strong> — 铸铁锅/石板，250℃预热，入炉喷水蒸汽，220℃烤25分钟</span></div>    </div>  </div>  <div class="impressions">    <div class="section-label">大家印象</div>    <h2 class="section-title">吃过的人怎么说</h2>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"终于找到一款吃完不会胃胀的面包，酸种发酵真的很不一样。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@茜茜</div>    </div>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"给孩子吃很放心，配料表干净得让人感动。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@豆豆妈</div>    </div>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"蜜香很足，但不是那种加了香精的甜，是真正蜂蜜的味道。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@美食爱好者 · 小林</div>    </div>    <div class="feedback-cta">      <a href="/feedback/" class="feedback-link">        分享你的印象        <span>→</span>      </a>    </div>  </div></div>]]></content>
    
    
