    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>.product-detail { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 24px 80px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; }.product-back { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6B6B6B; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 48px; transition: color 0.2s; }.product-back:hover { color: #0A0A0A; }.product-header { margin-bottom: 64px; }.product-eyebrow { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #C4713B; margin-bottom: 12px; }.product-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }.product-intro { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #6B6B6B; }.product-meta-bar { display: flex; gap: 40px; padding: 24px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); margin: 40px 0; }.product-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }.product-meta-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #6B6B6B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }.product-meta-value { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; }.section-label { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B6B6B; margin-bottom: 24px; }.section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 32px; }.ingredients-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }.ingredient-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); font-size: 0.9rem; }.ingredient-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); }.ingredient-name { font-weight: 400; }.ingredient-amount { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #6B6B6B; }.calorie-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }.calorie-box { background: #F0EDE8; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }.calorie-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: #C4713B; }.calorie-unit { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B6B6B; margin-top: 4px; }.steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }.step { display: flex; gap: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }.step-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #C4713B; min-width: 24px; }.impressions { margin-top: 80px; padding-top: 64px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.08); }.impression-card { background: #F0EDE8; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 16px; border-left: 3px solid #C4713B; }.impression-quote { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }.impression-author { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #6B6B6B; }.feedback-cta { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; }.feedback-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.15); color: #0A0A0A; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem; transition: all 0.25s; }.feedback-link:hover { border-color: #0A0A0A; background: #0A0A0A; color: #FAF9F7; }</style><div class="product-detail">  <a href="/" class="product-back">← 返回首页</a>  <div class="product-header">    <div class="product-eyebrow">酸种 · 天然酵母 · 欧包</div>    <h1 class="product-title">天然酵母<br>乡村面包</h1>    <p class="product-intro">养天然酵母是一件需要耐心的事。每天喂它，看着它长大、成熟、稳定，像养一只小宠物。酸种面包的酸味不是刺鼻的那种，是慢慢化开的麦香。乡村面包外脆内软，切开有漂亮的蜂窝气孔。</p>  </div>  <div class="product-meta-bar">    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">价格</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">¥42</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">热量</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">268 kcal / 100g</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">类型</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">欧包</span>    </div>    <div class="product-meta-item">      <span class="product-meta-label">份量</span>      <span class="product-meta-value">约400g/个</span>    </div>  </div>  <div class="ingredients">    <div class="section-label">配料</div>    <h2 class="section-title">每一项都有依据</h2>    <div class="ingredients-list">      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">高筋面粉</span><span class="ingredient-amount">350g · 筋度适中，支撑气孔</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">黑麦粉</span><span class="ingredient-amount">50g · 增加风味，延缓老化</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">天然酵母（鲁邦种）</span><span class="ingredient-amount">150g · 自养，零添加</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">水</span><span class="ingredient-amount">300g · 70%水含量，面团湿软</span></div>      <div class="ingredient-item"><span class="ingredient-name">盐</span><span class="ingredient-amount">9g · 2.2%，增强结构</span></div>    </div>  </div>  <div style="margin-top: 64px;">    <div class="section-label">热量参考</div>    <div class="calorie-grid">      <div class="calorie-box">        <div class="calorie-num">268</div>        <div class="calorie-unit">kcal / 100g</div>      </div>      <div class="calorie-box">        <div class="calorie-num">1070</div>        <div class="calorie-unit">kcal / 整份（约400g）</div>      </div>    </div>  </div>  <div style="margin-top: 64px;">    <div class="section-label">制作步骤</div>    <div class="steps">      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">01</span><span><strong>水解</strong> — 面粉+水混合，静置1小时</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">02</span><span><strong>加种</strong> — 加入天然酵母，捏散混合</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">03</span><span><strong>拉伸折叠</strong> — 室温26℃，每30分钟拉伸折叠一次，共4次</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">04</span><span><strong>一发</strong> — 静置发酵3-4小时</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">05</span><span><strong>分割整形</strong> — 倒扣出缸，分割200g一个</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">06</span><span><strong>二发</strong> — 室温继续发酵1小时，入冰箱冷藏过夜</span></div>      <div class="step"><span class="step-num">07</span><span><strong>烘烤</strong> — 铸铁锅250℃预热45分钟，230℃烤35分钟</span></div>    </div>  </div>  <div class="impressions">    <div class="section-label">大家印象</div>    <h2 class="section-title">吃过的人怎么说</h2>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"终于找到一款吃完不会胃胀的面包，酸种发酵真的很不一样。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@茜茜</div>    </div>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"外脆内软，酸种风味很足，不是那种刺鼻的酸，是慢慢化开的香。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@面包控 · 阿明</div>    </div>    <div class="impression-card">      <p class="impression-quote">"气孔很漂亮，切开的一瞬间就知道这是好面包。"</p>      <div class="impression-author">@烘焙爱好者 · 小雨</div>    </div>    <div class="feedback-cta">      <a href="/feedback/" class="feedback-link">分享你的印象 →</a>    </div>  </div></div>]]></content>
    
    
